title: New Vaccine Analysis Findings from Germany with Dr. Sabine Sebel
cleaned_text:
Dr. Sabine Sebel has a degree in Biology from the University of Freiburg in Germany, specialising in Cell Biology, Microbiology and Immunology. She has a PHD in genetics and Gain of Function. She has worked in the pharmaceutical industry, though hasn’t had much success as her ethics always trumped her desire to make money.

This is an edited segment from the weekly live General Assembly meeting on September 5, 2022. The full meeting is available here.
